(52, 'Arizona', 'Fleischer Scholars', '10?12', 'Students must be currently sophomores or juniors (so rising juniors or seniors) in Arizona high schools, interest in business, applying; competitive process.', 'Free / scholarship?supported: students admitted receive a free college course credit; program costs covered by Fleischer / partner institutions.', 'Annual application; ?Space ? is limited ? apply early.? For example, application cycles aligned to academic year; exact deadlines vary.', 'https://nasep.arizona.edu/resources/internships/fleischer-scholars-program', 'Academic Program', 'Math', 'Outside School', 'Immersive pre?college business program. Students engage with business leaders, network, develop entrepreneurial mindset. Delivered outside school (at ASU / partner settings). Offers prestige via college credit and business exposure. Selective because limited space. In?person.', '2025-11-12 02:58:02'),
