(78, 'Arkansas', 'Arkansas STEM Venture Academy', '9?10', 'Selection by school counselors / teachers / administrators; cohort model; students interested in STEM careers.', 'Varies; likely free or low cost since run via partnership; possible sponsorships; some travel if needed.', 'Announced by Arkansas STEM Coalition; times depend on district & cohort.', 'https://arkansasstemcoalition.com/programs/stem-venture-academy/', 'Academic Program', 'Multidisciplinary', 'Through School', 'Gives exposure to mid?skill STEM jobs; allows students to engage with industry partners; smaller cohort (~25 students) so more hands?on.', '2025-11-12 02:58:02'),
