(1126, 'Wisconsin', 'UW?Madison Summer Music Clinic', '6-8', 'open to all', '? $790 for commuter students\r\n? $1095 for residential students\r\n? Scholarships available', 'May 15', 'https://precollege.wisc.edu/summer-music-clinic/junior-session/', 'Academic Program', 'Arts', 'Outside School', '? A week-long immersive music program for middle school students interested in music.\r\n? Offered by University of Wisconsin-Madison', '2025-11-12 03:04:34'),
