(1285, 'Maine', 'Maine Center for Research in STEM Education', 'K-12 educators', 'K-12 educators.', 'The cost is $300 for a one-day training.', 'Applications received by January 6 will receive full consideration.', 'https://umaine.edu/risecenter/k-12/', 'Academic Program', 'STEM', 'At School', 'This center offers professional learning opportunities to K-12 educators to support STEM education.', '2025-12-03 00:17:53'),
